WEBVTT

00:02:27.419 --> 00:02:31.786
ili muongee miongoni mwenu na msiwe
na masikitiko kwa watu wengine.

00:02:31.810 --> 00:02:33.969
(Kicheko)

00:02:33.993 --> 00:02:35.394
Basi ndicho tunachofanya.

00:02:35.418 --> 00:02:38.910
Ni mfululizo tu wa makundi madogo,

00:02:38.934 --> 00:02:42.483
ambapo wanaume, wanawake, mashoga, wa
kawaida, wanandoa, wenye wenza,

00:02:42.507 --> 00:02:46.776
wanaweza kuongelea kuhusu mtu wao
aliyekufa,

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:48.046
na kusema vile vitu

00:02:48.070 --> 00:02:51.789
ambavyo mtu mwingine kwenye maisha yao
hayuko tayari kuvisikia bado.

00:02:51.813 --> 00:02:54.291
Eneo kubwa la mazungumzo.

00:02:54.315 --> 00:02:56.103
Kama, "Mme wangu alikufa wiki mbili
zilizopita,

00:02:56.127 --> 00:02:58.445
siwezi kuacha kufikiria kuhusu
ngono, ni kawaida?"

00:02:58.469 --> 00:02:59.623
Ndio.

00:02:59.647 --> 00:03:01.696
"Je kama ni mmoja wa
Property Brothers?"